# Task 04 - CoreTech FAQ Dataset and Rule-Based Chatbot

## Overview

This project contains a FAQ dataset and a rule-based chatbot developed for CoreTech.

The chatbot reads FAQ data from a CSV file, matches user questions using keywords, and returns relevant responses.

## Features

- FAQ dataset with 25+ questions and answers
- Keyword-based question matching
- User input handling
- Unknown question handling
- Continuous conversation support
- Exit command support

## Files

### coretech_faq.csv
Contains frequently asked questions and answers related to CoreTech services.

### chatbot.py
Python chatbot that reads the FAQ dataset and responds to user queries.

## Technologies Used

- Python
- Pandas
- CSV Dataset

